    "body": "Agreed, though Surrender and Leave are the only 2 ways to leave the match without closing the game. Now they behave differently what is also not ideal. Often players don't realize this difference, they simply leave as they know they lost to play another match, so it could improve the situation overall.\r\nI'll look at that PR."
